      p Interview: Reece Shearsmith & Steven Pemberton
    div.card__attribution.bbc-two
      span BBC Two

    div.card__duration
      i.icon.icon--duration
      span.js-duration
        | 00:00

  div.card__panel.js-panel
    p Donec eu nulla porta, pretium mi vitae, congue leo. Quisque id metus odio. Donec fermentum nibh mi, vitae consectetur orci mattis et. Sed dolor dolor, vestibulum vel nisl eu, gravida eleifend lorem.

